the overarching app state should know:
the current screen
on game play screen, a new game state should be generated
on leaving game play screen, the score of the current game should be in app state
ideally, you can only navigate from gameplay to game end screen
any wrong assumptions would reveal itself during implementation
when the game has ended, it should store the score of the last game

the app state should have a config property
which contains the dimensions for the board
duration per question
total questions



